In order to not lose balance in both wealth and in poverty and to be in motiveless happiness, it is necessary to act as an eternal being by centering on the eternal essence; then, wealth will not corrupt and poverty will not pervert.
Akif Manaf 
#yoga #yogaeskişehir #yogalife

If there is really no expectation, nothing that emerges will disturb the inner balance and disappoint.
Akif Manaf
